1) Example No 1 - Get 3 Candidates with least Exp

So We will use the below query in which we are Using ORDER BY and LIMIT, The Data Will be Assorted in the Ascending Order.


select student_id, enrollment_date, selected_course, student_fname, years_of_exp, student_company, batch_date, source_of_joining, location from student ORDER BY years_of_exp limit 3;


+------------+---------------------+-----------------+---------------+--------------+-----------------+------------+-------------------+-----------+
| student_id | enrollment_date     | selected_course | student_fname | years_of_exp | student_company | batch_date | source_of_joining | location  |
+------------+---------------------+-----------------+---------------+--------------+-----------------+------------+-------------------+-----------+
|          2 | 2024-02-03 20:40:37 |               1 | virat         |            3 | flipkart        | 5-02-2021  | linkedin          | hyderabad |
|          1 | 2024-02-03 20:40:37 |               2 | rohit         |            6 | walmart         | 5-02-2021  | linkedin          | bangalore |
|          4 | 2024-02-03 20:40:38 |               1 | rahul         |            8 | walmart         | 19-02-2021 | quora             | chennai   |
+------------+---------------------+-----------------+---------------+--------------+-----------------+------------+-------------------+-----------+








------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


2) Example No 2 - If we want the Assortment in Descending Order we will use below Query


SELECT student_id, enrollment_date, selected_course, student_fname, years_of_exp, student_company, batch_date, source_of_joining, location from student ORDER BY years_of_exp DESC LIMIT 3;


+------------+---------------------+-----------------+---------------+--------------+-----------------+------------+-------------------+----------+
| student_id | enrollment_date     | selected_course | student_fname | years_of_exp | student_company | batch_date | source_of_joining | location |
+------------+---------------------+-----------------+---------------+--------------+-----------------+------------+-------------------+----------+
|          7 | 2024-07-21 12:27:29 |               3 | carl          |           20 | wipro           | 19-02-2021 | youtube           | pune     |
|          6 | 2024-07-21 12:27:29 |               2 | brain         |           18 | tcs             | 5-02-2021  | youtube           | pune     |
|          5 | 2024-07-21 12:27:29 |               1 | kapil         |           15 | microsoft       | 5-02-2021  | friend            | pune     |
+------------+---------------------+-----------------+---------------+--------------+-----------------+------------+-------------------+----------+








